Privacy Policy for Color Chase
Effective Date: October 30, 2024

Color Chase  is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains that we do not collect, store, or use any personal information when you use our app.

1. Information We Collect
We do not collect any personal information from users of Color Chase. The app does not require or request any personally identifiable information (PII), nor does it track user behavior or use analytics tools.

2. Third-Party Services
Color Chase does not use any third-party services that collect personal information. The app is self-contained and does not connect to any external systems or services.

3. Children's Privacy
Color Chase does not collect any personal information from users, including children under the age of 13. The app is safe for all ages and complies with privacy laws.

4. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date. We encourage you to review this policy periodically for any updates.

